Files inherited from the upstream project (retained, with modifications
noted below; remain under the upstream MIT license)
=============================================================================

- SKILL.md
  The original file authored upstream. This fork rewrites it as a pure
  orchestration layer (upstream ~323 lines -> fork ~173 lines): removes the
  "search philosophy" preamble, removes the preflight `check-deps.sh`
  section, replaces the platform selection table with a "default-parallel /
  on-demand-join" matrix, renames the skill (`academic-search` ->
  `paper-search`), adds a personal-config reference, adds CNKI/WoS rows,
  and adds a three-file deliverable contract
  (`paper_raw/refs.ris` + `summary.md` + optional PDFs).

- scripts/cdp-proxy.mjs
  Byte-identical to upstream apart from two comment/log strings renamed
  from `academic-search` to `paper-search`.

- references/api-cookbook.md
  Upstream base. This fork extends it with stricter conventions
  (`ti:` + `abs:` as default on arXiv, explicit `datetype=pdat` date
  ranges on PubMed), more date-range examples, and a pointer to
  `scripts/download_arxiv.py` for batch PDF download.

- references/cdp-api.md
  Upstream base. This fork prepends a warning about the chrome-devtools
  MCP `evaluate_script` `args` field (must be element uids, not generic
  literals) and updates the proxy start-up path.

- references/site-patterns/arxiv.org.md
  Upstream base. This fork appends 2026-04-07 observations on Varnish
  429/503 cooldowns (60-90 s) and recommends `submittedDate:[...]` range
  syntax for time-window queries.

- references/site-patterns/scholar.google.com.md
  Upstream base. This fork adds a "search expression construction" section
  (nested boolean / no field prefixes / phrase quoting) with a concrete
  multi-concept example, and a stricter "time filter" section describing
  the lack of reliable publication-month metadata.

- references/site-patterns/dl.acm.org.md
- references/site-patterns/ieeexplore.ieee.org.md
- references/site-patterns/paperswithcode.com.md
- references/site-patterns/pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov.md
- references/site-patterns/semanticscholar.org.md
  Unchanged from upstream (only CRLF/LF normalization after the
  Windows checkout).

